2017.title: Qiskit
2017.description: Qiskit is an open-source software stack, primarily a Python-based SDK, for quantum computing that provides tools to build, optimize, and execute quantum programs on both quantum computers and classical simulators.

2017.title: Q-Sharp
2017.description: Q# is a high-level, open-source programming language developed by Microsoft for writing quantum programs. Q# is included in the Quantum Development Kit (QDK)
